import React from 'react';

export function IconoFacebook(props) {

            <g id="Icon_" data-name="Icon " transform="translate(14 14)">
                <rect id="Area-2" data-name="Area" width="20" height="20" transform="translate(-0.052)" fill="#fff" opacity="0"/>
            <g id="Icon" transform="translate(5.81 0.869)">
                <path id="Path" d="M15,1.667H12.5A4.167,4.167,0,0,0,8.333,5.833v2.5h-2.5v3.334h2.5v6.666h3.334V11.667h2.5L15,8.333H11.667v-2.5A.833.833,0,0,1,12.5,5H15Z" transform="translate(-5.833 -1.667)" fill="#fff" stroke="#1c2126" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.667"/>

        </svg>
    );
}
